“Get aboard our unique boat and experience a whole new dimension of accommodation. With modern amenities and a great view over the water, you can enjoy a unique stay unlike any other. Whether you're planning a short weekend getaway or a long-term stay, our boat offers the perfect balance of relaxation and adventure. Come and discover a new definition of waterfront relaxation on our charming boat.”
The boat is about 5 minutes from the city by Taxi.

name: Studio Tibastvägen
description:
Welcome to this dream studio! This modern gem, located in a charming villa, with generous 50 sqm you have plenty of space to create your own personal oasis. Equipped with state of the art appliances including induction stove, fridge/freezer and dishwasher make it easy to cook. Washer and dryer available

Sunny days you enjoy on your private south facing terrace, protected by an electric awning. Natural light pours in through large south position windows offering a lovely view and a warm atmosphere.
